{"tid":1860643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想講真係好撚多人支持醫護罷工","createTime":"2020-02-03T18:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T23:20:16.000Z","uid":84267,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d17175560fc1fef42e2f37d28823e223aa8228","tid":1860643,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"話說小弟喺外國，呢度無乜香港人<br />\n<br />\n今日搭巴士遇到三個50歲左右既香港人呀姨，講緊肺炎同醫護罷工<br />\n<br />\n咁佢地既歲數通常都係藍絲局多，所以我無特別出聲。<br />\n點撚知佢睇完全支持醫護手足罷工，完全理解情況，思路非常清晰。仲不停屌柒林鄭話佢係&ldquo;死八婆死都唔封關&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我更係加把嘴埋去啦，大家傾得幾撚開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>小事一樁，但我想同醫護手足講：<br />\n你地真係好多人支持架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算遠在外國，一班唔多上網，資訊唔流通既老人家都好支持你地做既野。</strong><br />\n<br />\n罷工最緊要<span style=\"color: orange;\">團結</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">團結</span>真係力量黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日二千幾人罷，高層已經嚇到瀨<span style=\"color: brown;\">屎</span>. <br />\n<br />\n口講影響唔大，又有小貓三四隻藍絲去頂，嗰少少人頂到二千幾人？你話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後又出封濕鳩email，唔驚就假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕秋後既，我雖然唔能夠不負責任講唔洗驚。<strong>但希望醫護手足千萬唔好妄自菲薄，認清自己既bargaining power同重要性</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n醫護本身已經唔夠人，我就唔撚信高層秋後足幾千人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聽日醫護吹雞集體情願，大家識做。撐爆個場佢，用行動支持醫護。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T1icqPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT1icqPa.jpg&h=baa36da1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0885154b4f5f2e53a22929599d2f8f78bb7c6f8","tid":1860643,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"醫護團結贏撚硬<br />\n柒婆醫管局一定要跪"},{"pid":"da4e1aa2522fb463d11acdcad67fd06b0ca70515","tid":1860643,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0885154b4f5f2e53a22929599d2f8f78bb7c6f8","tid":1860643,"uid":2054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:46:21.000Z","msg":"醫護團結贏撚硬<br />\n柒婆醫管局一定要跪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"醫護手足加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbb6d8416467deefe443e6934bf83c9c1ba6185e","tid":1860643,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:48:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19f3e25e194970778da158c38ca0315377807267","tid":1860643,"uid":92885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93a44dab4ffd8d6e9ee8f06c487ea9d86a06ae21","tid":1860643,"uid":275160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"屋企個藍絲呢獲都支持醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地真係好怕死<br />\n民心所向啊屌"},{"pid":"f6331e96d4cacc50df6661c76daccefe601b1135","tid":1860643,"uid":200663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:51:15.000Z","msg":"落到場啲人鬧梗係鬧班返工藍絲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似去一間唔夠人手嘅餐廳咁<br />\n啲客都唔會鬧啲冇返嘅 staff<br />\n係都搵樓面出氣啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f1e9012d7694e9104a224de359524115851e1a","tid":1860643,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:51:17.000Z","msg":"2千人罷都驚到係咁出聲明, 9千人罷會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713d70ad0598650c64f67defd8b90ce965f770c0","tid":1860643,"uid":84267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"93a44dab4ffd8d6e9ee8f06c487ea9d86a06ae21","tid":1860643,"uid":275160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:49:28.000Z","msg":"屋企個藍絲呢獲都支持醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地真係好怕死<br />\n民心所向啊屌"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T18:51: